window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Viola Wild has spent the last hundred years scourging the world to find the heir to the Eirikrsen's legacy.</p> <p>She doesn't expect her latest inquiry to be fruitful. Thomas Miller is just a human. How could he be linked to the most ancient and terrifying line of vampire this world has ever known?</p> <p>She soon realizes, there's more to the man and to his charming little sister.</p> <p>Blood From A Stone is a prequel novella to the series After Darkness Falls.</p>"; 
